    <h3>Disabling Non-Essential Cookies</h3>
    <p>Creators can disable non-essential cookies in three quick steps.</p>
    <p>1) Go to the <a href="https://gumroad.com/settings/third_party_analytics">Third-party analytics tab in your Settings</a></p>
    <p>2) Toggle off "Enable third-party analytics services" to disable cookies</p>
